              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_laser_treatment">Laser Therapy</xref>) uses intense, narrow beams of light to cut and destroy 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_tissue">TISSUE</xref>, such as cancerous 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_tissue">TISSUE</xref>.        </p>
